name: You and your partner will discuss a given topic. The examiner will ask you to share your opinions and experiences about daily routines, favorite activities, and future plans. You will also describe a memorable experience and explain why it was important to you.
questionContents: What is a hobby or activity you enjoy? Why do you like it?
Describe a memorable trip or event in your life. What made it special?
Talk about a goal you want to achieve in the future. How will you accomplish it?
Do you prefer working alone or in a team? Why?
If you could travel anywhere in the world, where would you go and why?
